Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:35.21,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)}It is currently the Great Age of Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.75,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}A struggle between countless pirates began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:40.34,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}while looking for the great treasure, One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.93,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}left behind by the legendary Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.93,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}The boy who became a rubber man after eating the Gomu Gomu Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.85,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Monkey D. Luffy, is one of the many adventurers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:51.27,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}who went out to sea to become the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:55.73,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Luffy and his companions have already experienced countless adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:03:00.61,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}Not even the World Government can ignore their existence any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.45,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:07.03,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What adventure is waiting for us next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.54,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Today, the crew aiming for the New World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:13.88,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}will continue through the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:23.12,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy lost his brother Ace in the great war against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.88,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,then he escaped to the Island of Women.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:28.75,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,There he was overwhelmed by an unbearable sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:34.66,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But now, we go back in time ten years, to East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:41.50,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,This story takes place when the brothers Luffy and Ace were still children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:46.91,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was left in the care of the Dadan Family, a group of bandits on Mt. Corvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:50.29,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,There he met Ace and Sabo, two troublemakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:53.00,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,They shared a toast of brotherhood together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:56.38,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Our bonds will keep us connected as brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.72,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,With this, starting today, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:02.88,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.51,Main,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:12.71,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become a pirate first, so that'll be impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:16.02,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!  I'm going to become a pirate before either of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:22.27,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,You two are still going on about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:27.98,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, you're gonna become marines!  Why is that so hard to understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:32.00,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,"We're moving out..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.36,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.24,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:44.34,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Our very own secret base!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.22,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.79,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The season changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:00.66,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:06.30,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!  He went that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.16,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.75,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on it!  We won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:15.16,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!  We've got him surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.00,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!  He's almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.68,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes... Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:44.12,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.41,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I did it... I got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:09.83,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,You did great, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.10,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,That's our second catch of the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.66,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll get to eat a lot of danpa soup! { def: danpa plays on panda... is it just its reversed color scheme or is there something more to it? }
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.15,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:18.39,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!  Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:21.20,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first ever catch!  Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.23,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.36,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!  Look behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:27.69,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:35.57,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,A tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.75,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,He must have followed the scent of our prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.71,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!  Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.41,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,He's after the danpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.86,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I killed this one myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.46,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:00.58,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,l-let you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:03.37,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,He's too strong for you!  Run away, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.44,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,No way!  Get lost, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.36,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't leave, I'll beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.88,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,That moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.15,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.83,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.01,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.96,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.04,Main,Ace & Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!  Wait!  Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.94,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run away while he's distracted by the prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:42.77,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.77,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back for you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.90,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that you lost your first ever catch like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:05.73,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest.  What else can we do when we're up against the Tiger Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:10.26,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,But I caught that one!  Why'd he have to take what wasn't his?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.76,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stupid!  Don't shake the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:20.86,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.21,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:44.60,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!  Hurry and pull us back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.44,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:49.91,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:56.45,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally back... We've had really bad luck today.  Let's just go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:59.51,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,We're back, but we're unlucky, huh? {TL: Pun: This could be interpreted as "We're back, but we're not back"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:01.68,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I sure am hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.84,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,And whose fault is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.10,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:10.53,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,But still, the first prey he'd ever caught got stolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.78,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,it's no wonder he got mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.50,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to fight the Tiger Lord is just far too reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.79,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.75,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:45.24,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Brothers sure are a nice thing to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:47.73,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,If the two of you were part of my crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:56.40,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, there's no need for you to get involved here. { def: i'm throwing flashbacks on these lines, thoughts may be more appropriate tho }
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.95,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Let us handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:01.16,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,No.  As the captain, I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:10.20,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,What're you laughing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.87,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Laughing won't fill your stomach, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.34,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:18.12,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, Sabo!  You should join my crew after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.38,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Right?  You'll join, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:20.93,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:24.43,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd agreed to decide that when we're older?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:29.05,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I think, it'd be much more fun if the three of us were together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.48,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You'll need my help.  Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:35.58,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd understand if you said that {\i1}you{\i0} needed {\i1}our{\i0} help, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:36.43,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:37.49,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.40,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be saving you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:43.45,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,If you two decided to join my crew, I'd let you join any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:44.87,Main,Sabo & Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,No, it'll be my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.91,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Then this conversation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:49.90,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You won't join me, no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.06,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.26,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:55.63,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be anyone's underling.  Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.44,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?  It would be fun, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.12,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:06.06,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,How about, the one who defeats that huge tiger gets to be captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:09.00,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Huge tiger?  Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:13.02,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,The chances of you becoming the captain are practically zero, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:15.18,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:19.06,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,None of us can beat that thing now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:20.39,Main,Ace & Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:22.53,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!  That settles it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:24.02,Main,Ace & Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,It's a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.17,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.34,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.57,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,We worked hard fishing these up... What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:43.93,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no choice.  This is bait to draw him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:49.95,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.52,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Greedy jerk!  We won't let you take them today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.45,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:07.88,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Is that the Tiger Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.56,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?  That's just some bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:17.08,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,How boring.  Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:22.34,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,No.  This guy is as strong as the Tiger Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:26.09,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't beat him, we won't stand a chance against the Tiger Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:31.73,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.  So he'll make for some excellent practice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:33.45,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:34.97,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,That's cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.15,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:10.10,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!  He won't calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.91,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.29,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:50.53,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That old guy's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:53.38,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,That's Naguri from the Gray Terminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.99,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!  He'll send you flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.73,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.36,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,Noshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:32.94,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't your den, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.95,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to the forest, noshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.91,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:02.52,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:10.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Visit us at http://www.yibis.com/
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:17.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chat us up at #yibis@irc.rizon.net
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:25.69,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Naguri, you were a pirate?!  Not only that, but a captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:29.90,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,I was indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:36.17,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!  Only a pirate captain could pull something like that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:37.51,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:42.95,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing that huge bear off just by glaring at him... You're just like Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:45.15,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You're incredible, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:47.38,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:51.76,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that Naguri used to be a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:53.93,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:58.47,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,He goes around collecting junk...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:01.40,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,and spending whole days hammering at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:04.66,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,trying to create some nonsensical device.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:11.05,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,The Gray Terminal residents and Bluejam's crew are always taunting him.  That's all I've ever seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.02,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,He was quite a pitiful oldtimer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:15.17,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a kid, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:16.94,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That's what a true pirate is like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:21.21,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a kid, too!  What do you know about pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:26.25,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I do know!  Shanks never picks meaningless battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.00,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.72,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.  This one's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.51,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:35.23,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,He got the bigger part!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:37.89,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,It's 'cause you were spacing out. {Uh, no, a larger bit just happened to land on your lap. You liar Sabo. I hate you forever now.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:38.69,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:43.52,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Naguri, you have some too.  It's your reward for saving us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.86,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:51.53,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is a pirate captain doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.28,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,You really want to know, noshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:00.66,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to tell us, then you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.62,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine, noshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:07.04,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of Gold Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:10.05,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:12.70,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I know of him!  The Pirate King, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:16.65,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,My crew challenged the Pirate King Roger to a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:17.59,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.82,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,...and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:22.64,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,We all went our separate ways after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:28.77,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,I kept drifting around as if I was rolling down a slope...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.49,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,and ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:35.20,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple story, but that's what happened, noshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:39.20,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,But you fought against the Pirate King, right?  That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:44.58,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, no... We were no match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:48.38,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,He completely beat us into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:53.88,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  So the Pirate King was so strong, even you couldn't beat him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:18:01.46,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... It wasn't just Roger.  His crewmates were all unbelievably strong, noshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:06.94,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,Their constant, flawless teamwork was the most impressive thing about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:10.56,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,We might have been enemies, but it was an honor to meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:19.78,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I've got a long way to go before I can become a true pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:23.41,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,You're interested in pirates, noshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.80,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.76,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:28.62,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!  A pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:32.04,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!  Pirate-oldtimer, can you train me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.18,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:38.66,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta become Ace and Sabo's captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.14,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,Their captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.30,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, right?  Be my Pirate-master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:44.70,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, noshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.98,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:50.07,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!  Then I'll be counting on you from tomorrow on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.59,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Where'd Ace go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:57.36,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.62,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The Pirate King is Ace's dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:06.58,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  But this is a secret, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:09.26,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Never say a word about this in front of Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.10,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, he'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.28,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:16.21,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the details... But anyway, he hates Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.47,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,But he's his dad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:21.13,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,So what if he's his dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:28.56,Flashbacks,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for you two but, even with parents, I'm still alone! {Copy-paste from 496}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:31.06,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Your parents were...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:35.61,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Not all kids get along with their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:39.74,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Still, he was the Pirate King and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:43.61,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you want to ask him about Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:46.03,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,but you mustn't say a word!  Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.96,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.71,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and you too, Naguri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:53.21,Main,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I understand, noshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:59.00,Thoughts,Naguri,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I never would've guessed he was Roger's son...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:05.72,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,There he is... Listen, you've gotta act ignorant, normal and casual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:06.40,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.72,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say a single word about–
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:09.52,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I won't!  Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:15.05,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ace!  So you went home before us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:19.32,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ace!  So Roger was your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:22.53,Thoughts,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:27.31,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Luffy!  I kept telling you not to bring that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:28.31,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:29.10,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:31.47,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:35.11,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,From Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.89,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ace!  What kind of guy was Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:39.84,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.35,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask him that, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.07,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blow our cover so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:45.07,Secondary,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Sabo!  I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.76,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:47.76,Secondary,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:52.25,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that name ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:58.14,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?  Don't be so stingy, just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.73,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to punch us out of the blue without any explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:01.90,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.45,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You could at least tell us something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.24,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:10.49,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!  Brothers don't keep secrets from each other, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.66,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!  What do you mean, brothers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.94,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!  Roger!  Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:16.88,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ace's dad, the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:19.40,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!  Don't provoke him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:23.09,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because you couldn't keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:25.99,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,What?!  What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:27.14,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:37.89,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, you two are no longer my brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:41.85,Main,Luffy & Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what I was gonna say!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:49.01,Main,Sabo's father,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:53.59,Main,Bluejam,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.  I'll leave no stone unturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:57.24,Main,Bluejam,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as you heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:21:59.24,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start looking immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:03.20,Main,Bluejam,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.  But if you do find him, don't grab him just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:08.33,Main,Bluejam,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?  We have to make sure that man winds up indebted to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:13.41,Main,Bluejam,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep him waiting, he'll be all the more grateful when we bring the kid back. { def: using "the kid" here.   }
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:15.70,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:20.23,Main,Bluejam,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch quietly until the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:24.07,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,"An important guest is arriving this spring"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:28.03,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Dogra, Magra!  Where is this Goa-place?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:35.81,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mt. Corvo, the Gray Terminal and Windmill Village all happen to be part of Goa Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:37.05,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.05,0:22:38.46,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:44.50,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,You hardly ever read the newspapers... Are pigs gonna fly today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.93,0:22:46.45,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:49.46,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,A guest will be coming to this kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:52.80,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to be making quite a fuss over this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:56.68,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,What's the commotion about?  Are they really so important...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:22:59.86,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,These Celestial Dragons or whatever they're called?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:08.80,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,After being trained by Naguri...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:11.45,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others finally challenge the great tiger to battle! { def: tlc: is the name different here from "Tiger Lord" earlier? }
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:12.71,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.71,0:23:13.84,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Showdown With the Great Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:15.47,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Who Will Be the Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:18.04,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
